channel.title: Vps help 667/711
channel.description:
i recently got a VPS for my 667/711 rsps and i cant get the VPS to work im using SSH client with CentOS here is my run:
[code]screen -A -m -d -S rsps java -Xmx512m -classpath bin:lib/*: com.rs.Launcher true true false [/code]
